Unitron/Firestarter:




Unitron let two charges intercept Hot Rod's missiles that were heading for 
him and pulled hard left, a photon charge striking him in the body causing a 
large gash, slightly slowing his speed.

---

Firestarter fired off flares to intercept the missiles, pulling up into the 
air letting the charges go under him harmlessly, all as he and Unitron got 
closer and closer to the CF's exposed bridge.
